<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Stormrise — Engineering Rain for a Thirsty World</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --sky: #0a1628;
    --deep: #060e1c;
    --slate: #1a2a40;
    --mist: #8faabf;
    --cloud: #c8d8e8;
    --light: #e8f2f8;
    --rain: #4a9bc4;
    --rain-bright: #72c4f0;
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-muted: #8a6e32;
    --white: #f5f2ee;
    --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    --serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    --sans: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--deep);
    color: var(--cloud);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(6,14,28,0.9) 0%, transparent 100%);
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-logo span { color: var(--rain-bright); }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mist);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--rain-bright); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0 3rem 6rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-canvas {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 120% 80% at 50% 0%, #1a3a5c 0%, #0a1628 45%, var(--deep) 100%);
  }

  /* Animated rain particles */
  .rain-layer {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .rain-drop {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(74,155,196,0.6));
    border-radius: 1px;
    animation: fall linear infinite;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  @keyframes fall {
    0%   { transform: translateY(-10vh); opacity: 0; }
    5%   { opacity: 1; }
    95%  { opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { transform: translateY(105vh); opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Cloud shapes */
  .cloud-layer {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 60%;
    z-index: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cloud-shape {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    filter: blur(40px);
    animation: drift linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes drift {
    from { transform: translateX(-5%); }
    to   { transform: translateX(5%); }
  }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 780px; }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block; width: 40px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--rain-bright);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--deep);
    background: var(--rain-bright);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.95rem 2.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--white); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .btn-ghost {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cloud);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,216,232,0.3);
    padding: 0.95rem 2.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--rain-bright); color: var(--rain-bright); }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2.5rem; right: 3rem; z-index: 2;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mist);
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .hero-scroll::after {
    content: '';
    width: 1px; height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--mist), transparent);
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── STATS BAND ── */
  .stats-band {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    background: rgba(10,22,40,0.8);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    position: relative;
  }

  .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .stat-num span { color: var(--rain-bright); }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mist);
  }

  /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
  section { padding: 7rem 3rem; }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-tag::before {
    content: '';
    display: block; width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--rain-bright);
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ── TECHNOLOGY ── */
  .tech-section {
    background: var(--sky);
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
  }

  .tech-intro {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem; align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .tech-desc { color: var(--mist); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; }

  .tech-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .tech-card {
    background: var(--sky);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    transition: background 0.4s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .tech-card:hover { background: var(--slate); }

  .tech-num {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tech-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .tech-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tech-body { color: var(--mist); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ── MISSION ── */
  .mission-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 8rem 3rem;
    background: var(--deep);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mission-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 55%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sky) 0%, #0d2040 100%);
    clip-path: polygon(10% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
  }

  .mission-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-text .section-tag { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .mission-lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .mission-quote {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--cloud);
    line-height: 1.45;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--rain);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .mission-visual {
    position: relative;
    padding: 3rem;
  }

  .mission-diagram {
    width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 1;
    position: relative;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }

  /* ── PROCESS ── */
  .process-section {
    background: var(--sky);
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
  }

  .process-header { max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-steps::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 28px; left: 14%;
    right: 14%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--rain), var(--rain), transparent);
    opacity: 0.3;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .process-step {
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,155,196,0.3);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
    background: var(--sky);
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-num::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 4px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,155,196,0.15);
  }

  .step-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-body {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── IMPACT ── */
  .impact-section {
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
    background: var(--deep);
  }

  .impact-header {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .impact-header h2 { max-width: 480px; margin-bottom: 0; }

  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: 280px 280px;
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .impact-card {
    background: var(--sky);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: default;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }

  .impact-card:hover { background: var(--slate); }

  .impact-card.large { grid-row: span 2; }

  .impact-card-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .impact-card-num span { color: var(--rain-bright); }

  .impact-card-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rain);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .impact-card-body {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .impact-card-bg {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30%; right: -10%;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 12rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
  }

  /* ── RESEARCH ── */
  .research-section {
    background: var(--sky);
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
  }

  .research-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .research-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }

  .research-item {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .research-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }

  .research-year {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
    min-width: 50px;
    padding-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .research-text h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .research-text p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--mist); }

  .research-visual {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: var(--slate);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* SVG cloud diagram in research */
  .cloud-diagram {
    width: 90%; height: 90%;
  }

  /* ── CAREERS ── */
  .careers-section {
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--deep) 0%, var(--sky) 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .careers-bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -5%;
    left: -2%;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(8rem, 18vw, 15rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .careers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .careers-content .section-tag { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .careers-content p { color: var(--mist); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  .open-roles {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px;
  }

  .role-item {
    background: rgba(26,42,64,0.8);
    padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .role-item:hover { background: var(--slate); }

  .role-title {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .role-dept {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
  }

  .role-arrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    transition: color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }

  .role-item:hover .role-arrow { color: var(--rain-bright); transform: translateX(3px); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--deep);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
  }

  .footer-top {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .footer-brand p {
    color: var(--mist);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    max-width: 280px;
  }

  .footer-col-title {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rain-bright);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .footer-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: var(--mist);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

  .footer-bottom {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-copy {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(143,170,191,0.5);
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(200,216,232,0.3);
  }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .animate-in {
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .delay-4 { animation-delay: 0.55s; }

  /* Intersection observer targets */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
  .revealed { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Storm<span>rise</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#technology">Technology</a></li>
    <li><a href="#mission">Mission</a></li>
    <li><a href="#research">Research</a></li>
    <li><a href="#impact">Impact</a></li>
    <li><a href="#careers">Careers</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" style="color:var(--rain-bright)">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-canvas">
    <!-- Cloud shapes -->
    <div class="cloud-layer">
      <div class="cloud-shape" style="width:600px;height:300px;top:5%;left:10%;animation-duration:18s;animation-direction:alternate;"></div>
      <div class="cloud-shape" style="width:400px;height:200px;top:15%;right:5%;animation-duration:22s;animation-direction:alternate-reverse;"></div>
      <div class="cloud-shape" style="width:800px;height:250px;top:30%;left:-5%;animation-duration:28s;animation-direction:alternate;opacity:0.5;"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Horizontal light shimmer at cloud base -->
    <div style="position:absolute;bottom:35%;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,rgba(74,155,196,0.15),transparent);"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Rain drops (JS generated) -->
  <div class="rain-layer" id="rainLayer"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow animate-in">Next-Generation Atmospheric Engineering</div>
    <h1 class="animate-in delay-1">
      We make the <em>sky</em><br>give back what we're owed.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub animate-in delay-2">
      Stormrise combines precision drone technology, advanced radar arrays, and AI-driven weather modeling to deliver controlled precipitation — ending drought one cloud at a time.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta animate-in delay-3">
      <a href="#technology" class="btn-primary">Explore the Technology</a>
      <a href="#mission" class="btn-ghost">Our Mission</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scroll">Scroll to explore</div>
</section>

<!-- STATS BAND -->
<div class="stats-band reveal">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">80<span>+</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">Years of cloud seeding science</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">15<span>%</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">Average precipitation increase</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">3.2<span>B</span></div>
    <div class="stat-label">People facing water scarcity</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-num">0</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Harmful byproducts</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TECHNOLOGY -->
<section class="tech-section" id="technology">
  <div class="tech-intro">
    <div>
      <div class="section-tag reveal">Technology</div>
      <h2 class="reveal">An integrated system.<br>A complete solution.</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="tech-desc reveal">
      Our platform modernizes a proven process through a tightly integrated triad of software, hardware, and data validation. Every component is engineered to work together — closing the loop from atmospheric detection to verified rainfall.
    </p>
